WEBVTT

00:02:30.895 --> 00:02:35.726
I don't need to care about anybody
or anything other than my nation.

00:02:36.465 --> 00:02:40.068
Usually, of course,
people have many identities

00:02:40.092 --> 00:02:42.514
and loyalties to different groups.

00:02:43.036 --> 00:02:47.840
For example, I can be a good patriot,
loyal to my country,

00:02:47.864 --> 00:02:51.102
and at the same time,
be loyal to my family,

00:02:51.126 --> 00:02:53.487
my neighborhood, my profession,

00:02:53.511 --> 00:02:54.971
humankind as a whole,

00:02:54.995 --> 00:02:56.599
truth and beauty.

00:02:57.370 --> 00:03:01.641
Of course, when I have different
identities and loyalties,